{"tid":1836070,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"正呀喂 因肺炎關係 多套強國賀歲片取消上映","createTime":"2020-01-23T05:40:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-23T14:03:01.000Z","uid":41343,"like":16,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"2f20aa7845e294f5629161ca226a0962559be870","tid":1836070,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T05:40:35.000Z","msg":"電影囧媽官微消息，電影《囧媽》宣布撤出春節檔，具體檔期待定。此前，電影《姜子牙》和《熊出沒&middot;狂野大陸》均宣布撤出春節檔。截至目前，共有三部電影宣布撤出春節檔。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://z1.dfcfw.com/2020/1/23/202001231324051376446492.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fz1.dfcfw.com%2F2020%2F1%2F23%2F202001231324051376446492.jpg&h=653342d2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"23e67356e95ff2cd453dd592a35c36a3a3bdb2db","tid":1836070,"uid":41343,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T05:41:38.000Z","msg":"1月23日，電影《姜子牙》宣布改檔，退出春節檔，擇日上映，成為繼《熊出沒&middot;狂野大陸》后第二部退出春節檔的影片。聲明中寫道：「如今疫情發生，我們亦當眾志成城，以防疫為重、以生命為重。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://newsimgs.sina.tw/article/images/news-15797538094492.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewsimgs.sina.tw%2Farticle%2Fimages%2Fnews-15797538094492.jpg&h=29073d47&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e2555e025487f3978af2c5d732dfb4c1d42ee750","tid":1836070,"uid":41343,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T05:42:36.000Z","msg":"電影《熊出沒&middot;狂野大陸》發佈公告，將正式退出春節檔，擇日再映。我們正在積極聯繫影院和票務平台妥善處理退票事宜，對您所造成的不便，在此向您真誠致歉。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://newsimgs.sina.tw/article/images/news-15797538097381.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewsimgs.sina.tw%2Farticle%2Fimages%2Fnews-15797538097381.jpg&h=cbcd539f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5908f4f24985c5e7efa02c64618ad12486bb16b4","tid":1836070,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T05:42:55.000Z","msg":"攬炒了"},{"pid":"4c17b12475b2b9f5a881c202f632f9b9078a83ca","tid":1836070,"uid":90392,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTim